# show only: kernels/ experiments/ models/ figures/ Readme.md
*
!kernels/
!kernels/**
!experiments/
!experiments/**
!models/
!models/**
!figures/
!figures/**
!Readme.md
!.gitignore

# drop compiled/cache inside tracked dirs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.ptx
**/*.cubin
**/*.fatbin
**/*.egg-info/
